  <brief_title>An Investigational Drug Study to Assess Weight Loss in Obese and Overweight Patients (0364-037)(TERMINATED)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Clinical Trial to Study the Safety and Efficacy of Taranabant (MK0364) in Obese Patients and in Overweight Patients With Obesity-Related Co-Morbidities, Followed by a 1-Year Extension</official_title>
  <sponsors>
