  <source>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A 1 year worldwide study in obese and overweight patients to assess the safety and effect on
      body weight of an investigational weight loss drug.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
    The overall profile does not support development for obesity
  </why_stopped>
